casebody.data:
Tuesday, May 16, 1995

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

93-2153. Johnson v. Cleveland Clinic Found. Franklin County, No. 93AP-1032.

This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application be, and the same is hereby, granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed, effective May 15, 1995.
